resolution: "Fixed the feasible combined branch scope: duplicate close reason autofill, container child rollups, linked-test pipe/sandbox ergonomics, audit-update retry guidance, esbuild security override, coverage expansion and threshold ratchet, plus tracker evidence/backlog items."
